simplesect.title: Description
simplesect.para: Look at each table. If the table is enabled and its countdown counter times out, add dwell data to dwell packet until a packet delay is reached or the dwell packet is completed. If dwell packet is completed, send the packet and reset the counter.

simplesect.title: Description
simplesect.para: Copy memory value from a single dwell address to a dwell packet.

parameterdescription.para: identifies dwell entry within specified table (0..)
if copy was performed successfully; non-zero otherwise.

simplesect.title: Description
simplesect.para: Send contents of memory pointed to by a table as a telemetry packet.

parameterdescription.para: Identifies source dwell table for the dwell packet.

simplesect.title: Description
simplesect.para: Initialize parameters used to control generation of dwell packets.

parameterdescription.para: Identifies source dwell table for the dwell packet.
